1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,129
Persons who reach the top rungs in business management, selling, engineering, religious work,

2
00:00:06,240 --> 00:00:16,849
writing, acting, and in every other pursuit, get there by following conscientiously and continuously a plan for self-development and growth.

3
00:00:17,440 --> 00:00:23,409
Any training program, and that's exactly what this book is, must do three things.

4
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:26,770
It must provide content, the what to do.

5
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:30,690
Second, it must supply a method, the how to do it.

6
00:00:30,880 --> 00:00:36,369
And third, it must meet the ACID test, that is, get results.

7
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:45,090
The what of your personal training program for success is built on the attitudes and techniques of successful people.

8
00:00:45,359 --> 00:00:47,649
How do they manage themselves?

9
00:00:47,760 --> 00:00:49,970
How do they overcome obstacles?

10
00:00:50,160 --> 00:00:52,450
How do they earn the respect of others?

11
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:55,169
What sets them apart from the ordinary?

12
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:56,530
How do they think?

13
00:00:57,119 --> 00:01:03,250
The how of your plan for development and growth is a series of concrete guides for action.

14
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,570
These are found in each chapter.

15
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,090
These guides work.

16
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:09,570
Apply them and see for yourself.

17
00:01:10,160 --> 00:01:12,690
What about the most important part of training?

18
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:13,649
Results?

19
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:23,810
Wrapped up briefly, conscientious application of the program presented here will bring you success and on a scale that may now look impossible.

20
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:31,649
Broken down into its components, your personal training program for success will bring you a series of rewards.

21
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:38,290
The reward of deeper respect from your family, the reward of admiration from your friends and associates,

22
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:47,169
the reward of feeling useful, of being someone, of having status, the reward of increased income and a higher standard of living.

23
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:50,129
Your training is self-administered.

24
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:55,250
There will be no one standing over your shoulder telling you what to do and how to do it.

25
00:01:55,599 --> 00:02:00,129
This book will be your guide, but only you can understand yourself.

26
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:04,369
Only you can command yourself to apply this training.

27
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:07,169
Only you can evaluate your progress.

28
00:02:07,599 --> 00:02:12,050
Only you can bring about corrective action should you slip a little.

29
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:17,889
In short, you are going to train yourself to achieve bigger and bigger success.

30
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:23,090
You already have a fully equipped laboratory in which you can work and study.

31
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:25,810
Your laboratory is all around you.

32
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:29,169
Your laboratory consists of human beings.

